reprimanded the teenager for speeding after the nearaccident but 
had not hit him 
he said kennedy visited the teenager later to clarify 
matters but that he did not apologize for anything mahoney could 
not say whether kennedy had pushed avila 
kennedy 36 was elected last month to his second term in 
congress he is the eldest son of the late sen robert kennedy and a 
