oct 1 last year us corn sales to the soviet union totaled 
slightly less than 52 million tons 
a metric ton is about 2205 pounds and is equal to 394 bushels 
of corn or 367 bushels of wheat or soybeans the 750000 tons of 
corn would be about 295 million bushels 
