virus that causes aids in the united states and the african hiv2 
virus from a 37yearold woman from the ivory coast 
the viruses cause a variety of diseases including acquired 
immune deficiency syndrome aids from hiv1 has killed about 45000 
people so far in the united states but hiv2 has been found here in 
only one west african patient visiting the united states the hiv2 
strain has been primarily limited to west africa and parts of europe 
