in the lower rio grande valley said his saucedas precision 
grinding inc in san benito constantly stays busy on one recent 
afternoon his shop was producing quality control gauges for the 
199091 models of an automobile manufacturer he chose not to 
identify with skills he brought back from his years in chicago 
they are skills he realizes his native region lacks 
this is not an industrial area sauceda said its 
agricultural the areas just starting to be industrial 
john heath who operates tentex tool and supply co in laredo 
said he could double his business if he had the skilled toolanddie 
workers 
